casebody.data:
TENNESSEE WINE AND SPIRITS RETAILERS ASSOCIATION, petitioner,
v.
Zackary W. BLAIR, Interim Director of the Tennessee Alcoholic Beverage Commission, et al. No. 18-96. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 4, 2019.

Motion of Illinois, et al. for leave to participate in oral argument as amici curiae and for divided argument granted. Joint motion of respondents for divided argument denied.
